          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Farm Support Integrity for Family Farms Act </b></p> <p>The bill modifies Department of Agriculture commodity programs with respect to: (1) payment limitations, and (2) the requirement to be actively engaged in farming in order to receive payments. </p>]]></text>
